definition.text: There was a problem trying to send your contribution to your fork of the Superalgos repository, or from your fork to the Superalgos/Superalgos main repository.

paragraphs.text: Check the following section for details on what may have happened. After you fix the issue that prevented the App Contribute Command to run, you may try again.
In the following section you will find the specific information received when this error occured.
You will only see it if you opened this page as a result of the error actually happening.
